Program 2: Factorial Using Function
def fact(n):
    f = 1
    for i in range(1, n+1):
        f *= i
    return f

print(fact(5))
Output
120

Program 3: OOP Example
class Student:
    def __init__(self, name):
        self.name = name

    def show(self):
        print("Name:", self.name)

s = Student("Sanjana")
s.show()
Output
Name: Sanjana

